ervice->productcatalogservice\",\n    \"frontend->productcatalogservice\",\n    \"cartservice->redis\",\n    \"checkoutservice->shippingservice\",\n    \"checkoutservice->emailservice\",\n    \"checkoutservice->cartservice\"\n  ],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"productcatalogservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"error_ratio\",\n      \"evidence\": \"状态组合显示：frontend调用productcatalogservice时出现连接拒绝错误（connection refused），错误码14，表明productcatalogservice服务不可用\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"productcatalogservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"checkoutservice->productcatalogservice调用延迟异常：正常10.5秒，异常时9.1秒（虽然略有下降，但绝对延迟仍很高），同时出现3次异常\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"cartservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\", \n      \"evidence\": \"checkoutservice->cartservice调用延迟显著增加：GetCart从2.5秒增加到7.1秒（2.9倍），EmptyCart从2.4秒增加到18.7秒（7.8倍）\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"redis\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"cartservice->redis的HMSET操作延迟从1.6秒增加到9.6秒（6.1倍），表明Redis存储层存在性能问题\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"shippingservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"checkoutservice->shippingservice的ShipOrder操作延迟从225ms增加到1.1秒（5倍），GetQuote操作也有延迟增加\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"emailservice\", \n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"checkoutservice->emailservice的SendOrderConfirmation操作延迟从699ms增加到809ms-2.2秒（1.2-3.1倍）\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n## 关键发现总结：\n\n1. **根因服务**: `productcatalogservice` 出现连接拒绝错误，这是最直接的故障表现\n2. **传播路径**: productcatalogservice的故障影响了checkoutservice和frontend服务\n3. **连锁反应**: 由于checkoutservice的异常，导致其下游服务（cartservice、shippingservice、emailservice）都出现延迟增加\n4. **存储层问题**: Redis的HMSET操作延迟显著增加，表明存储层也存在性能瓶颈\n\n**建议进一步调查**: productcatalogservice的健康状态和Redis存储性能，这两个组件可能是问题的根本原因。", "metric_analysis_findings": "```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_metric_keys\": [\n    \"client_error_ratio\",\n    \"error_ratio\",\n    \"rrt_max\",\n    \"requ